1
00:00:05,820 --> 00:00:11,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Hellhorde and Imperial Army have been 
locked in battle for many years.</i></font>

2
00:00:11,940 --> 00:00:15,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Led by their grand inquisitor, 
Torture Tortura,</i></font>

3
00:00:15,460 --> 00:00:18,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>the Hellhorde's elite inflict 
their torture on a daily basis.</i></font>

4
00:00:18,650 --> 00:00:23,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She faces fierce beasts, flames, 
unknown devices and spells,</i></font>

5
00:00:23,410 --> 00:00:26,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>yet the princess does not give in.</i></font>

6
00:00:26,330 --> 00:00:28,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She would never give in.</i></font>

7
00:00:28,240 --> 00:00:32,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She would never let the words, 
"I surrender!" leave her lips so readily.</i></font>

8
00:00:32,930 --> 00:00:38,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Meanwhile, the princess's former friend, 
the assassin Sakura Heartrock,</i></font>

9
00:00:38,680 --> 00:00:44,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>fails to assassinate the Hell-Lord, 
and sets off on a new path.</i></font>

10
00:00:56,440 --> 00:00:59,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sakura-chan, 'tis finally time 
for your first torture.</font>

11
00:00:59,900 --> 00:01:01,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will you really be okay on your own?</font>

12
00:01:01,820 --> 00:01:05,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. I feel like I'd lean 
on your help with you there.</font>

13
00:01:06,010 --> 00:01:08,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, time to give it my all.</font>

14
00:01:11,010 --> 00:01:14,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've committed a lot 
of terrible deeds in my past.</i></font>

15
00:01:15,550 --> 00:01:17,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So to make amends...</i></font>

16
00:01:18,270 --> 00:01:19,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>from here on out...</i></font>

17
00:01:21,610 --> 00:01:24,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll make people happy through torture!</font>

18
00:01:24,930 --> 00:01:26,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

19
00:01:32,880 --> 00:01:35,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Princess?</font>

20
00:03:04,200 --> 00:03:05,950
<font size="20"><b><font color="#d01c76">{\an8}<font size="32">'Tis Time for <font color="#020000">"Torture,"
<font color="#cf1374">Princess</font></font></font></font></b></font>

21
00:03:06,780 --> 00:03:07,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ex.</font>

22
00:03:08,600 --> 00:03:10,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've made up my mind.</font>

23
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:13,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will never give in to their torture!</font>

24
00:03:13,730 --> 00:03:15,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, if I haven't heard that before.</font>

25
00:03:15,720 --> 00:03:18,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This time, I'm dead serious.</font>

26
00:03:18,130 --> 00:03:20,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which is why I'm giving you this.</font>

27
00:03:21,480 --> 00:03:22,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A lightning amulet.</font>

28
00:03:22,970 --> 00:03:26,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This allows you to activate 
a lightning spell with your mind.</font>

29
00:03:26,930 --> 00:03:30,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The moment you think, "Her Highness 
is gonna cave to the torture,"</font>

30
00:03:30,140 --> 00:03:30,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

31
00:03:30,710 --> 00:03:33,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you can fire a lightning spell at me.</font>

32
00:03:33,190 --> 00:03:37,190
<font size="20"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font size="25"><font color="#725352">Agh</font></font></b></font></font>

33
00:03:34,290 --> 00:03:37,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The pain will help me 
regain my composure...</font>

34
00:03:37,010 --> 00:03:38,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've calmed down.</font>

35
00:03:38,420 --> 00:03:40,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and I'll be able to 
hold off on surrendering.</font>

36
00:03:40,990 --> 00:03:43,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that the only way 
you can control yourself?</font>

37
00:03:45,210 --> 00:03:48,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where'd this thing come from, anyway?</font>

38
00:03:48,270 --> 00:03:51,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After a torture the other day, 
while we were on a stroll,</font>

39
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:54,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I got a tour of the Hellholm armory.</font>

40
00:03:54,030 --> 00:03:56,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A tour of their armory 
in the middle of a stroll?!</font>

41
00:03:56,270 --> 00:03:57,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For an enemy nation's princess?!</font>

42
00:03:57,880 --> 00:04:02,510
<font size="20"><b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="35"><b><font color="#ed6e97">Hmph</font></b></font></font></b></font>

43
00:03:59,110 --> 00:03:59,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmph!</font>

44
00:03:59,870 --> 00:04:02,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just goes to show how much they trust me!</font>

45
00:04:02,850 --> 00:04:05,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's when I secretly 
borrowed the amulet.</font>

46
00:04:05,410 --> 00:04:07,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Betraying their trust...</font>

47
00:04:11,130 --> 00:04:12,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're sure about this?</font>

48
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:14,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, go ahead.</font>

49
00:04:14,930 --> 00:04:17,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do I have it in me, though?</font>

50
00:04:17,920 --> 00:04:21,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To fire a lightning spell 
at Your Highness?</font>

51
00:04:21,260 --> 00:04:22,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rest assured.</font>

52
00:04:22,750 --> 00:04:26,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After making up my mind, 
I won't be folding so easily.</font>

53
00:04:31,830 --> 00:04:33,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Princess.</font>

54
00:04:34,180 --> 00:04:36,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">'Tis time for torture.</font>

55
00:04:36,570 --> 00:04:39,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This will be your torture for today...</font>

56
00:04:40,150 --> 00:04:41,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fried chicken.</font>

57
00:04:41,420 --> 00:04:43,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks yummy!</font>

58
00:04:47,250 --> 00:04:49,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-Is something wrong, Princess?</font>

59
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:52,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-No, not at all.</font>

60
00:04:53,110 --> 00:04:54,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice going, Ex.</font>

61
00:04:54,940 --> 00:04:56,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was able to stay strong, thanks to you.</font>

62
00:04:56,910 --> 00:04:58,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Glad to hear it.</font>

63
00:04:58,580 --> 00:05:02,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were going on like, 
"Do I have it in me?"</font>

64
00:05:02,690 --> 00:05:04,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yet you didn't hesitate to activate it.</font>

65
00:05:04,590 --> 00:05:07,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I, too, was surprised 
at my complete lack of resistance.</font>

66
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:10,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you really okay?</font>

67
00:05:11,330 --> 00:05:13,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry about me.</font>

68
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:16,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perhaps you should ask 
the same of yourself.</font>

69
00:05:16,520 --> 00:05:19,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right, I <i>do</i> love fried chicken.</font>

70
00:05:19,620 --> 00:05:20,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However...</font>

71
00:05:21,030 --> 00:05:23,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you know which piece is my favorite?</font>

72
00:05:24,070 --> 00:05:28,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Verily, fried chicken comes 
in a variety of pieces.</font>

73
00:05:28,960 --> 00:05:31,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The thigh, popular for 
its fatty dark meat.</font>

74
00:05:32,050 --> 00:05:35,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The wing, with its chewy 
eating experience.</font>

75
00:05:35,740 --> 00:05:38,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And more, all with their own appeal.</font>

76
00:05:38,740 --> 00:05:41,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the piece that you're most fond of...</font>

77
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:43,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">'Tis none other than...</font>

78
00:05:43,930 --> 00:05:44,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The drumstick!</font>

79
00:05:44,770 --> 00:05:45,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You got it!</font>

80
00:05:50,970 --> 00:05:53,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What in the world has 
been going on today?</font>

81
00:05:53,650 --> 00:05:56,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry about it...</font>

82
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:58,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right on the money.</font>

83
00:05:58,350 --> 00:06:00,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love drumsticks.</font>

84
00:06:00,840 --> 00:06:03,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The way they look gets me so excited.</font>

85
00:06:04,210 --> 00:06:07,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It <i>is</i> the shape you 
associate most with chicken.</font>

86
00:06:07,480 --> 00:06:10,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Incidentally, the meal 
that I purchased today</font>

87
00:06:10,610 --> 00:06:13,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">happened to contain only 
a single drumstick.</font>

88
00:06:13,630 --> 00:06:14,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In other words...</font>

89
00:06:14,980 --> 00:06:20,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After I eat this one, 
there will be no drumsticks left.</font>

90
00:06:21,110 --> 00:06:23,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Wait, I give in. I'll talk!</font>

91
00:06:25,660 --> 00:06:27,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is for Her Highness's sake!</font>

92
00:06:27,660 --> 00:06:31,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will steel my heart 
and carry out my duty to the end!</font>

93
00:06:31,270 --> 00:06:32,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You monster!</font>

94
00:06:32,900 --> 00:06:36,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What is this, Princess? 
You're glowing!</font>

95
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:40,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Th-This is the strongest strike so far!</i></font>

96
00:06:40,330 --> 00:06:42,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I feel like I'll pass out 
if I drop my guard!</i></font>

97
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:47,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>However, I'm the Princess and 
Commander of the Imperial Third Legion!</i></font>

98
00:06:47,930 --> 00:06:49,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A measly lightning strike like this...</i></font>

99
00:06:54,220 --> 00:06:57,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cannot stop me from surrendering!</font>

100
00:06:55,310 --> 00:07:02,310
<font size="20">{\an8}<b><font face="Georgia"><font size="25"><font color="#141619">Surrender by Might</font></font></font></b></font>

101
00:06:58,200 --> 00:07:01,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Try using that iron willpower 
to endure the torture instead!</font>

102
00:07:02,850 --> 00:07:05,690
<font size="20"><font size="15"><b><font color="#1a191c">{\an8}The princess
confessed</font></b></font></font>

103
00:07:08,200 --> 00:07:09,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Delicious!</font>

104
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:12,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Drumsticks are the best!</font>

105
00:07:12,010 --> 00:07:14,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They just scream "chicken" to me!</font>

106
00:07:14,460 --> 00:07:17,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you like to try 
the other pieces, Princess?</font>

107
00:07:17,170 --> 00:07:19,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? Awesome!</font>

108
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:22,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love fried chicken!</font>

109
00:07:25,660 --> 00:07:30,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's imperial custom to eat egg 
dishes around the end of the year.</font>

110
00:07:32,470 --> 00:07:35,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Makes you wonder how it got started.</font>

111
00:07:36,220 --> 00:07:40,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've also bought the items you asked for.</font>

112
00:07:40,960 --> 00:07:42,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With biscuits?</font>

113
00:07:42,650 --> 00:07:47,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course, and vanilla 
ice cream to go with them.</font>

114
00:07:49,260 --> 00:07:52,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must be a mind reader.</font>

115
00:07:55,200 --> 00:08:03,210
<font size="20"><b><font color="#d01c76">{\an8}<font size="22">'Tis Time for <font color="#020000">"Torture,"<font color="#cf1374">Princess</font></font></font></font></b></font>

116
00:07:55,450 --> 00:08:00,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Torture planned to use 
the leftover chicken for rice pilaf,</i></font>

117
00:08:00,470 --> 00:08:02,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but there was none left in the end.</i></font>

118
00:08:08,540 --> 00:08:11,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>An experimental spell went haywire...</i></font>

119
00:08:12,130 --> 00:08:17,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>splitting up Torture into good 
and evil personalities.</i></font>

120
00:08:19,500 --> 00:08:23,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right now, my good self is trying 
to find a way to turn us back.</font>

121
00:08:24,260 --> 00:08:28,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So for today's torture, it'll be me,</font>

122
00:08:28,510 --> 00:08:30,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the evil Torture, who's in charge!</font>

123
00:08:31,440 --> 00:08:34,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Time for your torture, Princess!</font>

124
00:08:34,400 --> 00:08:37,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your evil self still shows up 
for work, huh?</font>

125
00:08:37,470 --> 00:08:39,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not really sure what makes her evil.</font>

126
00:08:39,630 --> 00:08:42,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For today's torture...</font>

127
00:08:42,240 --> 00:08:44,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Straight out of a plastic bag?!</font>

128
00:08:44,910 --> 00:08:47,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Torture I know would never do that!</font>

129
00:08:47,430 --> 00:08:49,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So this is evil Torture!</font>

130
00:08:49,670 --> 00:08:52,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pretty low bar for "evil," 
don't you think?</font>

131
00:08:52,460 --> 00:08:57,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you really think I'd yield 
to such slapdash torture?</font>

132
00:08:58,450 --> 00:08:59,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take a look!</font>

133
00:08:59,870 --> 00:09:01,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is your torture!</font>

134
00:09:01,750 --> 00:09:02,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An éclair!</font>

135
00:09:04,930 --> 00:09:06,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness!</font>

136
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:09,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Number one... It's number one...</font>

137
00:09:10,490 --> 00:09:14,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are all sorts 
of great pastries out there,</font>

138
00:09:14,500 --> 00:09:20,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but taking everything into account, 
like taste, availability, and price...</font>

139
00:09:20,450 --> 00:09:23,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The number one, tried-and-true pastry 
that won't let you down...</font>

140
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:25,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is a convenience store éclair!</font>

141
00:09:25,890 --> 00:09:29,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That light, crispy dough, 
thickly coated in chocolate...</font>

142
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:33,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And filled with a rich, gooey custard!</font>

143
00:09:33,260 --> 00:09:35,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perfect in every way!</font>

144
00:09:35,410 --> 00:09:38,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You may be evil, but 
you're still Torture!</font>

145
00:09:38,060 --> 00:09:40,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the perfect torture!</font>

146
00:09:40,050 --> 00:09:40,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

147
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:43,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think she feels 
as strongly as you do.</font>

148
00:09:44,630 --> 00:09:47,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want it... I want to eat it!</font>

149
00:09:47,420 --> 00:09:49,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However!</font>

150
00:09:49,450 --> 00:09:53,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the Princess and Commander 
of the Imperial Third Legion!</font>

151
00:09:53,370 --> 00:09:55,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will not give in to your torture!</font>

152
00:09:55,690 --> 00:09:57,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will not crave that éclair!</font>

153
00:09:57,900 --> 00:09:59,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah! You tell her, Your Highness!</font>

154
00:09:59,890 --> 00:10:01,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about?</font>

155
00:10:01,280 --> 00:10:02,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

156
00:10:02,210 --> 00:10:05,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I got one for you, too, 
so let's enjoy them together.</font>

157
00:10:05,450 --> 00:10:06,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

158
00:10:06,490 --> 00:10:09,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll give it to me even though 
I haven't surrendered?</font>

159
00:10:09,400 --> 00:10:10,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about the torture?</font>

160
00:10:10,510 --> 00:10:11,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right.</font>

161
00:10:11,870 --> 00:10:14,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm supposed to get 
a secret out of you for the torture.</font>

162
00:10:16,880 --> 00:10:18,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, whatever.</font>

163
00:10:18,520 --> 00:10:19,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Well, whatever?!"</font>

164
00:10:19,890 --> 00:10:22,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't I say I'm the evil Torture?</font>

165
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:24,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My feelings come before the rules.</font>

166
00:10:24,940 --> 00:10:27,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And nothing beats sharing some 
good food with other people!</font>

167
00:10:27,980 --> 00:10:31,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">E-Evil Torture!</font>

168
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:33,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Time to eat!</font>

169
00:10:36,940 --> 00:10:38,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yummy!</font>

170
00:10:38,170 --> 00:10:39,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is great!</font>

171
00:10:39,570 --> 00:10:41,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The chocolate's not too sweet, either!</font>

172
00:10:41,450 --> 00:10:43,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so gooey!</font>

173
00:10:43,410 --> 00:10:46,330
<font size="20"><b><font size="15"><font color="#363736">The 
Next Day</font></font></b></font>

174
00:10:47,730 --> 00:10:53,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I managed to return to normal, 
but my head still hurts from yesterday.</font>

175
00:10:54,550 --> 00:10:58,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My evil self technically 
wrote up a report...</font>

176
00:10:58,960 --> 00:11:00,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but it's completely incoherent.</font>

177
00:11:02,220 --> 00:11:05,100
<font size="20"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#2a3234">Dear Usual Torture</font></font></font>

178
00:11:03,060 --> 00:11:04,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A letter?</font>

179
00:11:05,180 --> 00:11:08,350
<font size="20">{\an7}<font color="#fefefc">m 0 0 l 200 0 200 40 0 40</font></font>

180
00:11:05,180 --> 00:11:08,350
<font size="20">{\an7}<font size="15"><font color="#525755"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>The evil Torture said
she didn't need it,
but since the éclair was good,
here's a secret for you.</b></font></font></font></font>

181
00:11:06,340 --> 00:11:08,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Dear usual Torture,</i></font>

182
00:11:08,700 --> 00:11:11,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The evil Torture said she didn't need it,</i></font>

183
00:11:11,570 --> 00:11:14,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but since the éclair was good,
here's a secret for you.</i></font>

184
00:11:15,570 --> 00:11:19,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All clownfish are born as males.</i></font>

185
00:11:20,590 --> 00:11:22,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How honorable of her.</font>

186
00:11:22,770 --> 00:11:25,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Princess.</font>

187
00:11:26,110 --> 00:11:28,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I may not be able to remember it...</font>

188
00:11:28,570 --> 00:11:30,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I seem to have had fun as well.</font>

189
00:11:28,580 --> 00:11:32,000
<font size="20"><font color="#464649">"Torture" Report Form</font></font>

190
00:11:28,580 --> 00:11:32,000
<font size="20"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font size="35"><font color="#222428">It was totally
 awesome</font></font></b></font></font>

191
00:11:34,730 --> 00:11:37,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like you're back 
to your usual self, Torture.</font>

192
00:11:37,470 --> 00:11:40,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Allow me to apologize 
for the inconvenience.</font>

193
00:11:40,620 --> 00:11:42,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, I've had enough.</font>

194
00:11:42,860 --> 00:11:46,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are all of these 
experimental spells going haywire?</font>

195
00:11:46,630 --> 00:11:49,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, there's a reason for that.</font>

196
00:11:49,620 --> 00:11:51,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What, you're here to make excuses?</font>

197
00:11:51,800 --> 00:11:53,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go ahead, let's hear them.</font>

198
00:11:54,970 --> 00:12:01,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Currently, Hellhorde R&D is experimenting 
with treating lumbago via electrotherapy.</font>

199
00:12:01,490 --> 00:12:07,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But a lightning amulet they were using
has gone missing from the armory,</font>

200
00:12:07,290 --> 00:12:11,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">leading to calibration issues that
have resulted in these frequent errors.</font>

201
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:12,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

202
00:12:13,770 --> 00:12:15,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A what amulet?</font>

203
00:12:15,590 --> 00:12:17,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">'Tis a lightning amulet.</font>

204
00:12:20,540 --> 00:12:21,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah.</font>

205
00:12:22,420 --> 00:12:27,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So it's not as though R&D is 
frivolously causing all this mayhem...</font>

206
00:12:27,390 --> 00:12:31,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Um, uh, well...</font>

207
00:12:31,150 --> 00:12:33,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me, I've been paged.</font>

208
00:12:33,560 --> 00:12:36,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be back when 'tis time 
for your torture, Princess.</font>

209
00:12:43,230 --> 00:12:45,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think it'd be best if you apologized.</font>

210
00:12:47,530 --> 00:12:49,990
<font size="20"><font size="15"><b><font color="#1a191c">{\an8}The princess
apologized</font></b></font></font>

211
00:12:52,950 --> 00:12:55,000
<font size="20"><b><font color="#d01c76">{\an8}<font size="22">'Tis Time for <font color="#020000">"Torture,"
<font color="#cf1374">Princess</font></font></font></font></b></font>

212
00:12:55,590 --> 00:12:59,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've committed a lot 
of terrible deeds in my past.</i></font>

213
00:13:00,040 --> 00:13:01,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So to make amends,</i></font>

214
00:13:03,050 --> 00:13:04,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>from here on out...</i></font>

215
00:13:06,150 --> 00:13:09,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll make people happy through torture!</font>

216
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:10,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

217
00:13:17,310 --> 00:13:19,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Princess?</font>

218
00:13:21,470 --> 00:13:24,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, is that you, Sakura?</font>

219
00:13:25,270 --> 00:13:27,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sakura? The Sakura that we know?</font>

220
00:13:27,950 --> 00:13:31,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure of it,  although it was hard to 
tell at first with that outfit...</font>

221
00:13:32,250 --> 00:13:34,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sakura, you...</font>

222
00:13:45,220 --> 00:13:46,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're alive?</font>

223
00:13:52,350 --> 00:13:53,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a relief.</font>

224
00:13:55,670 --> 00:13:58,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why, Princess?</font>

225
00:14:00,850 --> 00:14:04,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was deceiving you the whole time!</font>

226
00:14:05,440 --> 00:14:07,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I could tell.</font>

227
00:14:07,150 --> 00:14:08,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your attack that day...</font>

228
00:14:09,830 --> 00:14:13,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was a strike full of hesitation 
that lacked your usual commitment.</font>

229
00:14:15,310 --> 00:14:17,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That told me everything.</font>

230
00:14:18,790 --> 00:14:22,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew that deep down, 
you didn't want to kill me.</font>

231
00:14:23,170 --> 00:14:27,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I could see it in your eyes.</font>

232
00:14:27,640 --> 00:14:29,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That you had no choice in the matter.</font>

233
00:14:31,050 --> 00:14:33,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was the same for me.</font>

234
00:14:36,630 --> 00:14:38,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't have a choice in the matter.</font>

235
00:14:39,500 --> 00:14:40,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which is why...</font>

236
00:14:41,650 --> 00:14:44,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so relieved to see 
that you're alive and well.</font>

237
00:14:45,600 --> 00:14:47,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Princess...</font>

238
00:14:47,800 --> 00:14:49,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

239
00:14:50,800 --> 00:14:54,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. I had no choice in the matter.</font>

240
00:14:55,650 --> 00:15:00,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That said, I truly 
enjoyed our time together.</font>

241
00:15:01,620 --> 00:15:03,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All that time, I couldn't 
help but think...</font>

242
00:15:09,170 --> 00:15:14,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How nice it'd be 
if we were really friends.</font>

243
00:15:15,760 --> 00:15:17,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sakura.</font>

244
00:15:19,070 --> 00:15:20,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've also always...</font>

245
00:15:23,040 --> 00:15:24,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness?</font>

246
00:15:24,910 --> 00:15:25,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

247
00:15:27,190 --> 00:15:29,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's see if you can get 
the rest out of me.</font>

248
00:15:30,300 --> 00:15:32,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're an inquisitor now, aren't you?</font>

249
00:15:33,650 --> 00:15:36,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Show me what you can 
do with your torture!</font>

250
00:15:40,850 --> 00:15:42,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

251
00:15:48,040 --> 00:15:53,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We may have had a painful past, 
but now things are different.</i></font>

252
00:15:53,970 --> 00:15:55,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We're no longer from rival nations.</i></font>

253
00:15:56,320 --> 00:15:58,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm just a prisoner, 
and she's my torturer.</i></font>

254
00:15:59,250 --> 00:16:04,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's nothing strange about a prisoner 
and her torturer being friends.</i></font>

255
00:16:05,260 --> 00:16:07,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Isn't that right, Sakura?</i></font>

256
00:16:08,190 --> 00:16:10,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's amazing, Sakura!</font>

257
00:16:11,030 --> 00:16:12,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you practice that a lot?</font>

258
00:16:13,060 --> 00:16:18,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After a torture, you're supposed to 
complete a report immediately after.</font>

259
00:16:18,830 --> 00:16:22,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'll make an exception this once 
and give her an extension.</font>

260
00:16:25,030 --> 00:16:27,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The princess talked.</i></font>

261
00:16:28,310 --> 00:16:31,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Just her and Sakura, late into the night.</i></font>

262
00:18:04,970 --> 00:18:09,980
<font size="20"><b><font color="#f1f3f2">Hellholm Happy Farm</font></b></font>

263
00:18:05,510 --> 00:18:11,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, I never imagined you were 
the one Sakura had failed to assassinate.</font>

264
00:18:11,570 --> 00:18:13,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I sure was surprised.</font>

265
00:18:13,870 --> 00:18:15,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry, Sakura-chan.</font>

266
00:18:15,910 --> 00:18:16,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no.</font>

267
00:18:16,990 --> 00:18:20,950
<font size="20"><b><font color="#f0f4f7"><font size="10">Hellholm Happy Farm</font></font></b></font>

268
00:18:16,990 --> 00:18:20,950
<font size="20"><b><font color="#f0f4f7"><font size="10">Petting Zoo</font></font></b></font>

269
00:18:17,250 --> 00:18:20,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm to blame as well 
for omitting the details.</font>

270
00:18:20,930 --> 00:18:24,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I'm sure there's 
a lot we still have to talk about...</font>

271
00:18:24,580 --> 00:18:27,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But let's forget all that for today...</font>

272
00:18:27,090 --> 00:18:29,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and have fun at the farm!</font>

273
00:18:27,120 --> 00:18:35,340
<font size="20">{\an8}<b><font size="15"><font color="#edf0ef">Hellholm Happy Farm
 Petting Zoo</font></font></b></font>

274
00:18:29,220 --> 00:18:32,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>To celebrate the princess 
and Sakura's reconciliation,</i></font>

275
00:18:32,890 --> 00:18:35,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>they're taking a group trip to a farm.</i></font>

276
00:18:35,330 --> 00:18:36,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness!</font>

277
00:18:36,620 --> 00:18:38,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't run off in excitement
or you might trip!</font>

278
00:18:38,900 --> 00:18:40,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know!</font>

279
00:18:54,180 --> 00:18:55,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A goat!</font>

280
00:18:55,700 --> 00:18:57,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So cute.</font>

281
00:18:57,090 --> 00:18:59,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is my first time at a farm.</font>

282
00:18:59,890 --> 00:19:01,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mine as well.</font>

283
00:19:01,770 --> 00:19:06,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The empire's not without farms,
but they have handlers to do all the work.</font>

284
00:19:06,790 --> 00:19:08,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone.</font>

285
00:19:08,170 --> 00:19:10,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're selling animal food over there.</font>

286
00:19:10,630 --> 00:19:12,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanna feed them!</font>

287
00:19:12,750 --> 00:19:15,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here's some food for you.</font>

288
00:19:15,850 --> 00:19:17,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Feel free to take more.</font>

289
00:19:18,800 --> 00:19:20,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it good?</font>

290
00:19:22,330 --> 00:19:24,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're so adorable!</font>

291
00:19:25,730 --> 00:19:28,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? You're not gonna 
feed them, Princess?</font>

292
00:19:28,800 --> 00:19:33,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I never even looked 
after my own steed.</font>

293
00:19:33,750 --> 00:19:37,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I don't have any experience 
feeding large animals.</font>

294
00:19:38,310 --> 00:19:41,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a little scared now that 
I've come face-to-face with them.</font>

295
00:19:41,880 --> 00:19:42,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

296
00:19:43,320 --> 00:19:44,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How pathetic.</font>

297
00:19:44,640 --> 00:19:45,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

298
00:19:45,580 --> 00:19:47,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I'm sorry!</font>

299
00:19:47,420 --> 00:19:50,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now that I can be honest with you, 
I blurted out how I really feel!</font>

300
00:19:50,580 --> 00:19:52,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's how you feel about me?!</font>

301
00:19:53,100 --> 00:19:55,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Hey, I can do it, too!</font>

302
00:20:20,150 --> 00:20:23,650
<font size="20"><b><font color="#d8cabf">Hands-On Milking</font></b></font>

303
00:20:33,180 --> 00:20:35,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're good at this, Sakura.</font>

304
00:20:37,460 --> 00:20:38,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How was it?</font>

305
00:20:39,150 --> 00:20:41,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was my first time...</font>

306
00:20:41,490 --> 00:20:44,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it was warm, squishy, and fuzzy!</font>

307
00:20:44,460 --> 00:20:46,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Squishy and fuzzy?!</font>

308
00:20:48,480 --> 00:20:49,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right!</font>

309
00:20:49,780 --> 00:20:51,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's squishy and fuzzy!</font>

310
00:20:51,900 --> 00:20:54,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Squishy 'n' fuzzy!</font>

311
00:20:53,080 --> 00:20:55,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Your Highness, your face! Your face!</font>

312
00:21:01,820 --> 00:21:03,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This milk's amazing!</font>

313
00:21:03,520 --> 00:21:05,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can really tell that it's fresh.</font>

314
00:21:05,540 --> 00:21:06,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So creamy!</font>

315
00:21:08,740 --> 00:21:11,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It really is delicious.</font>

316
00:21:13,040 --> 00:21:17,920
<font size="20"><b><font size="12"><font color="#fdfcfd">Soft-Serve Ice Cream
Made with Fresh Milk</font></font></b></font>

317
00:21:13,040 --> 00:21:17,920
<font size="20"><b><font face="Georgia"><font size="12"><font color="#a92d32">Pork-Wrapped 
Rice Balls</font></font></font></b></font>

318
00:21:13,210 --> 00:21:17,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They have a store that sells soft-serve 
ice cream using the same milk.</font>

319
00:21:17,920 --> 00:21:20,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd love to try it, but...</font>

320
00:21:20,180 --> 00:21:23,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a little too chilly out 
to be eating soft serve.</font>

321
00:21:23,950 --> 00:21:25,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want some!</font>

322
00:21:26,370 --> 00:21:28,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maomao-chan's full of energy!</font>

323
00:21:29,330 --> 00:21:31,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me go and buy some, then.</font>

324
00:21:31,990 --> 00:21:33,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who here wants some soft serve?</font>

325
00:21:38,270 --> 00:21:40,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I do, too, of course.</font>

326
00:21:42,740 --> 00:21:44,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is great!</font>

327
00:21:44,300 --> 00:21:46,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so rich and creamy.</font>

328
00:21:48,280 --> 00:21:52,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Sakura-chan, you tried 
to assassinate Princess-chan?</font>

329
00:21:52,440 --> 00:21:53,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes...</font>

330
00:21:53,660 --> 00:21:55,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She even got a slash in.</font>

331
00:21:55,690 --> 00:21:57,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh...</font>

332
00:21:57,370 --> 00:22:00,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pretty wild. I mean, you two 
are friends now, right?</font>

333
00:22:04,710 --> 00:22:07,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah! Friends!</font>

334
00:22:07,210 --> 00:22:08,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Awesome!</font>

335
00:22:08,500 --> 00:22:09,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mm-hmm.</font>

336
00:22:10,480 --> 00:22:12,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Big news, everyone!</font>

337
00:22:13,060 --> 00:22:15,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It looks like there's 
a giant maze over there!</font>

338
00:22:15,720 --> 00:22:17,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was the one who found it.</font>

339
00:22:17,260 --> 00:22:19,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's all go check it out!</font>

340
00:22:19,030 --> 00:22:19,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

341
00:22:19,850 --> 00:22:21,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can't skip out on that!</font>

342
00:22:21,400 --> 00:22:25,400
<font size="20"><font face="Impact"><b><font color="#e6eef3"><font size="15">Maze Adventure</font></font></b></font></font>

343
00:22:21,680 --> 00:22:23,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get a move on!</font>

344
00:22:41,330 --> 00:22:45,210
<font size="20"><font size="14"><b><font color="#353438">{\an8}They're all
 great friends</font></b></font></font>

345
00:22:46,690 --> 00:22:49,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sakura... Sakura.</font>

346
00:22:50,670 --> 00:22:52,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sakura.</font>

347
00:22:55,060 --> 00:22:56,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're here.</font>

348
00:22:56,710 --> 00:22:58,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Oh...</font>

349
00:22:59,480 --> 00:23:00,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning.</font>

350
00:23:01,980 --> 00:23:03,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning, Sakura-chan.</font>

351
00:23:03,700 --> 00:23:06,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I slept like a baby.</font>

352
00:23:06,060 --> 00:23:08,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We <i>did</i> play lots today!</font>

353
00:23:08,110 --> 00:23:11,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, you were out like a light.</font>

354
00:23:11,490 --> 00:23:12,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take a look.</font>

355
00:23:14,420 --> 00:23:16,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Asleep and completely defenseless!</font>

356
00:23:16,940 --> 00:23:20,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not very assassin-like of you.</font>

357
00:23:20,570 --> 00:23:23,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like you weren't asleep, too. 
You just happened to wake up first.</font>

358
00:23:23,590 --> 00:23:25,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! You-chan!</font>

359
00:23:25,210 --> 00:23:28,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I got a photo of her. Look.</font>

360
00:23:28,110 --> 00:23:28,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

361
00:23:30,260 --> 00:23:31,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right!</font>

362
00:23:31,190 --> 00:23:33,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In-chan!</font>

363
00:23:34,010 --> 00:23:37,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not very commander-like of you.</font>

364
00:23:38,470 --> 00:23:41,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh, I can't believe I was drooling!</font>

365
00:23:41,650 --> 00:23:44,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Delete it! I'm begging you!</font>

